all 同底位sh put<br />\n<br />\n其中一面穿太多 都死"},{"pid":"a151a12d3ed25635dabe88651237394ee766e08c","tid":583823,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T15:20:07.000Z","msg":"option 會砍單??<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be2b6d515658bdb8cc88743289a7bc1a87cefd35","tid":583823,"uid":71970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a151a12d3ed25635dabe88651237394ee766e08c","tid":583823,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T15:20:07.000Z","msg":"option 會砍單??<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T15:31:29.000Z","msg":"會 特別係做short<br />\n如果你做short 錯方向 期權變ITM時 保證金會增加<br />\n佢個case 應該係爆其中一面 保證金增加時 自己嘅錢唔夠<br />\n咁就會比人斬倉<br />\n<br />\n做指數真係要夠錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除此之外 長假期前你果間broker都有機加你保證金"},{"pid":"1e5de1deb573f787cec755f82768a64bc21655a3","tid":583823,"uid":71970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5058f746e09452df607ac0e46f5ea49b5a9f70c0","tid":583823,"uid":69924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05fd04aee05f610ea54b5113aac0529d396789aa","tid":583823,"uid":150523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a7ab136e3e69074702fc535e4962fbb986d3257","tid":583823,"uid":71970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T14:16:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180306/1309116/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180306%2F1309116%2F&d=DRiYCPtFnkLeQ%2Ftp453ZXqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=f898ca17\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180306%2F1309116%2F&h=23129bc0\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180306/1309116/</a><br />\n<br />\n今年2月6日因為美股大跌，台灣期貨市場爆發一場期貨選擇權大屠殺，其中有一位受災戶，本金5000萬，卻在當天賠掉了1.2億元，等於賠了台北市一棟豪宅。<br />\n<br />\n這些上百名受災戶，受傷程度，從數百萬、數千萬到上億元，有些受災戶更泣訴，幾乎都已跟期貨商「簽了本票」，幾乎是傾家蕩產。<br />\n<br />\n其中最慘的一位李姓大戶，也到現場，雖然不願曝光，但他接受《蘋果》記者訪問時說，他做的是「價差單」，這類價差單是比較「保守」的，就是去賺兩個指數間的價差，例如看準指數不會漲破1萬點、及跌破9000點，去賺中間這1000點的價差。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">若以選擇權來說，就是各賣了一個「買權」和「賣權」</span> ，但當天開盤後，卻瞬間出現買賣權，全部拉到漲停、和跌停價位的現象，導致期貨商瞬間砍單，投資人蒙受鉅額損失。<br />\n<br />\n該大戶說，他保證金已經賠光了，現在只能等期貨商來「假扣押」，但他強調，只要期貨商有動作，他一定提告。<br />\n<br />\n另外還有受災戶在康和期下單，則痛批康和期內部風控有問題，「在跌破擔保維持率75%時，竟然沒有簡訊或電話通知」，沒有任何告知下，就直接砍單，導致他損失了上百萬元。（廖珮君／台北報導）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我有冇睇錯? 佢即係SC SP左 <br />\n其中一面爆左<br />\nIV升 margin又升 call margin好正常<br />\n比唔到錢就被人斬倉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T14:19:20.000Z","msg":"冇睇錯，short strangle 做大左，一舖清袋"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T15:14:59.000Z","msg":"開左高位sh call 同底位sh put<br />\n<br />\n其中一面穿太多 都死"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T15:32:14.000Z","msg":"好心佢做 spread好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇保護一野輸身家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"025f9ee5af457aa807632f0e42b5b54fd7f89df3","tid":583823,"uid":166288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T16:44:33.000Z","msg":"Short 兩邊收租<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一下大波幅兩邊爆哂, 收十幾次租, 一次輸突曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nShort 兩邊不如Long兩邊好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c372338b967ed870bd129b8271d0e4da3e5cbf0","tid":583823,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"025f9ee5af457aa807632f0e42b5b54fd7f89df3","tid":583823,"uid":166288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T16:44:33.000Z","msg":"Short 兩邊收租<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一下大波幅兩邊爆哂, 收十幾次租, 一次輸突曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nShort 兩邊不如Long兩邊好過啦<img src=\"/as